        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "If you worship a deity, this golden amulet transforms into your deity's religious symbol when you invest it. You gain a +1 item bonus to Religion. The symbol casts dim light in a 20-foot emanation.",
        "level": 3,
        "traits": [
